<h2><b>What is the purpose of this event?</b></h2>
<p>This academic meeting is designed to foster an increased and deeper understanding of lean improvement in healthcare,
    with a focus on academic teaching hospitals around the world. An international call for abstracts will be the basis
    for program design, with more than half of the program dedicated to delegate contribution. Delegate contribution may
    occur through oral presentation or poster format. <a href="#">Click here</a> for more information on the Call for Abstracts.
    Abstract submissions close <b>Friday July 14, 2017</b>.
</p>

